ygData.messageBody:
"O" levels, remind me of my birthday last year which fell exactly on the bio
practical. Get to practice my "parang skills" that day by "chopping" bull's eye
and then, gana hold up in the AVA room for several hours, by the time I reach
home, was already 7:00pm. Too tired to even blow out the candles of my
cake......
